text.tspan: Disease burden from lead exposure, 1990 to 2019
Disease burden is measured in disability-adjusted life years (DALYs). DALYs include years of life lost due to
premature death and years lived with a disability. One DALY equals one lost year of healthy life.
Source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease
